data.event: Its built-up (or metro) area, made of Yongkang City and Wuyi County, was home to 1,073,389 inhabitants at the 2010 census.
In 2003, Yongkang GDP ranked 47th out of over 1000 counties nationwide in China.
In 1992, the State Council approved the county to city.
